## Recommended Starting Standard

```
// Your "PseudoScript" format
FUNCTION functionName(parameter1, parameter2) {
    SET variableName = value

    IF condition THEN {
        DO action
    } ELSE IF otherCondition THEN {
        DO differentAction  
    } ELSE {
        DO defaultAction
    }

    FOR EACH item IN collection {
        PROCESS item
    }

    WHILE condition IS TRUE {
